[Cite as 02/09/2004 Case Announcements, 2004-Ohio-462J

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 9, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-0120. In re La. B.

Cuyahoga App. No. 81981, 2003-Ohio-6852. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal involving termination of parental rights/adoption. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of the court of appeals’ judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents.
